'''''Monster Manual II 1st edition''''' is a 1{{st}}-edition ''Advanced Dungeons & Dragons'' accessory.
{{Quote|''"the most complete alphabetical listing and description of the latest AD&D&trade; game creatures"''

''A must for the serious AD&D&trade; game player. This manual contains all the new members, from [[Abishai]] to [[Zygom]], including new creatures like the [[Deadly pudding|Deadly Pudding]], [[Deva]]s, and Valley Elves. And you'll also have the advantage of the extended lists of [[lycanthropes]], [[giant]]s, and other beasts.''}}
